1.9.0 (2026-07-23)
  - NEW: driving-status icons in the status bar's right cluster, just left of the
    settings gear — WIDE / LANDSCAPE TRACKS ONLY (both hidden entirely on the tall
    track: portrait / ⅓ slice). Live source (RadioFace/CarFmLive) re-synced; new
    ANDROID §4.6 + §4.1 right-cluster note + §8 motion bullet + README surface 1 +
    CORRECTION-LOOP step 3b.
    - GPS lock: an angled satellite (body ~28°, dish + downward signal arcs). Lit
      interactive-blue on a fix; with NO fix it is NOT greyed — styled like a disabled
      tell (§4.1 tells): full text color at ~32% opacity + the same faint 1px emboss.
      Always present (communicates lock state).
    - Vehicle in motion: a car with trailing motion lines, AMBER (fixed safety-color
      family, like TA — never the blue accent), pulsing SLOWLY (~2.6s, gentler than
      TA's ~1.1s). Rendered ONLY while in motion — absent (not dimmed) when stopped.
    - Prototype toggles: new `gpsLocked` and `inMotion` boolean tweaks on CarFmLive.
  - CHANGED DEFAULT: the hero Display Call Sign / Display Frequency options (§6.4) now
    default OFF for a station that HAS a logo → a logo-only hero by default (the logo
    fills the card); either can be turned back on per station. No-logo stations are
    unaffected (always show call sign + frequency). Reverses the 1.8.0 default.
    §4.2/§4.5/§6.4 + README surface 1/5 updated.
  - CHANGED: no-logo preset tiles AND prev/next peek cards restyled. The generated
    monogram cube is replaced by a WIDE colored box in the SAME landscape aspect as the
    real-logo plate, with the 4 call letters INSIDE the box and the frequency BENEATH it
    (call sign no longer repeated below the box). Peek cards now use the EXACT same
    treatment as the bottom preset tiles (real-logo image, or call-sign box + freq).
    Preset/peek frequency darkened to full text color + heavier weight for glance-
    legibility. §4.3/§4.5/§5 + README surface 1 updated.
  - Settings §6.3: removed the stale Tuner-source list (Si470x FM dongle / rtl_tcp —
    retired) and merged the two TUNER bullets into one describing the shipping set
    (connection status + RETRY/Details, source picker RTL-SDR · NWD/NOWADA · FYT/DuduOS
    · Auto, Start-radio-on-boot). Matches SettingsPanel + README surface 4.
  - Reference-screenshot note (still true, now also covers the new elements): the
    per-surface PNGs in screenshots/ predate 1.8 and show the OLD monogram cubes with
    NO driving-status icons. Do NOT diff the real-logo hero, the no-logo call-sign
    boxes, or the GPS/motion icons against those PNGs — they render live from
    CarFmLive.dc.html; trust the live render + ANDROID §4.5/§4.6 over the stale stills.

1.8.1 (2026-07-21)
  - Hero real-logo now GROWS to reclaim freed space when the per-station Display Call
    Sign / Display Frequency options (§6.4) are off: one element hidden → larger box,
